  "keyFeatures": [
    "One-command bootstrap via `npx @lidr/lidr-specboot` that copies all templates and recreates symlinks safely",
    "Multi-copilot support: single source-of-truth standards exposed to Claude, Cursor, GitHub Copilot, and Gemini simultaneously",
    "Symlink-based portability — agent-specific paths (.claude/, .cursor/) point to canonical ai-specs/ sources",
    "Pre-built AI agent definitions for backend developer, frontend developer, and product strategy analyst roles",
    "Reusable skill library (enrich-us, code-auditing, commit, using-git-worktrees, writing-skills, and more)",
    "Opinionated development standards: TDD, 90%+ test coverage, strict TypeScript, Clean/DDD architecture",
    "OpenSpec workflow integration: /enrich-us → /ff → /apply → /verify → /adversarial-review → /archive → /commit",
    "Optional MCP integrations for Jira ticket enrichment and Playwright E2E testing"
  ],
